Proven from `Mathlib.NumberTheory.Chebyshev.theta_le_log4_mul_x`, which
provides `θ x ≤ log 4 · x` for all `x ≥ 0`.  We take `C_θ := log 4`. -/
theorem chebyshev_theta :
    ∃ Cθ : ℝ, 0 < Cθ ∧
      ∀ t : ℝ, 2 ≤ t →
        (∑ p ∈ Finset.filter Nat.Prime (Finset.Iic ⌊t⌋₊),
