      -- d ∣ a (hypothesis), a ∣ M ⟹ M = a · (M/a) = (a/d) · d · (M/a).
      -- So M/d = (a/d) · (M/a).  Since b ∣ (M/a) (from a · b ∣ M and gcd(a,b)=1):
