    -- **Sub-claim**: M_d · d · b / M ≤ y^{-c}/2 · b (requires M ≥ 2 · M_d · d · y^c).
    -- This is the "L₀ sufficiently large" step (paper §7.4 line 1980-1985: P = exp(y_R^{A-1}) dominates).
    -- Closure path (multi-fire):
