    -- 1. From hP_bound at index k+1 (need k+1 < L - √L - 4, restrict L₀ if needed):
    --      exp(y_{k+2}^{A-1}) ≤ outer_P, where y_{k+2} = exp(tower(√L+k+1)/B).
