    -- 5. p ∤ primorial(⌊exp(y_target^A)⌋₊) (since p > ⌊exp(y_target^A)⌋₊), but p ∣ primorial outer_P.
    --    Combined with primorial(⌊exp(y_target^A)⌋₊) ∣ primorial outer_P:
    --      primorial outer_P ≥ primorial(⌊exp(y_target^A)⌋₊) · p.
